{"title":"Win a One-of-a-Kind Scott Spark RC; Nino Schurter Will Deliver","link":"https://bikerumor.com/win-this-one-of-a-kind-scott-spark-rc-hand-painted-by-lionel-smit/","date":1772818080000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659011-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_06-dd961b-original-1772533114-1536x1024.jpg\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"One of a kind Scott Spark RC benefits World Bicycle Relief\" /></p>\n<p>Scott, in collaboration with World Bicycle Relief, is giving away a hand-painted Spark RC race bike. Well, actually, those aren’t the only collaborators. Also working on the project is South African artist Lionel Smit and the GOAT, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/nino-schurter-spark-rc-x-n1no-goat-sram-chain/\">Nino Schurter</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike is being raffled off, with Nino personally handing it to the winner.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>One-of-a-Kind Scott Spark RC</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659010-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_03-ba2124-original-1772533114.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1025\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659010-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_03-ba2124-original-1772533114-1536x1025.jpg\" alt=\"One of a kind Scott Spark RC benefits World Bicycle Relief\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659010-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_03-ba2124-original-1772533114-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659010-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_03-ba2124-original-1772533114-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659010-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_03-ba2124-original-1772533114-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659010-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_03-ba2124-original-1772533114-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659010-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_03-ba2124-original-1772533114-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659010-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_03-ba2124-original-1772533114-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659010-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_03-ba2124-original-1772533114-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n<figcaption>Photos by Michael Riehle</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There will only be two bikes, but each is unique. Scott provided artist Lionel Smit with raw carbon Spark RC frames. Niono will keep one for his personal collection, and the other will go to the winner. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Scott emphasizes that these are not graphics or paint concepts. Rather, this is original art–ride it or display it on a wall! </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lionel Smit is known for his figurative portraits, paintings, and sculptures. However, painting a mountain bike frame is new for the artist.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659015-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_07-c52803-original-1772533114-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"2303\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659015-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_07-c52803-original-1772533114-1536x2303.jpg\" alt=\"One of a kind Scott Spark RC benefits World Bicycle Relief\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659015-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_07-c52803-original-1772533114-1536x2303.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659015-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_07-c52803-original-1772533114-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659015-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_07-c52803-original-1772533114-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659015-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_07-c52803-original-1772533114-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659015-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_07-c52803-original-1772533114-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659015-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_07-c52803-original-1772533114-1366x2048.jpg 1366w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659015-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_07-c52803-original-1772533114-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659017-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHL_13-7c08ae-original-1772533115.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"2303\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659017-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHL_13-7c08ae-original-1772533115-1536x2303.jpg\" alt=\"One of a kind Scott Spark RC benefits World Bicycle Relief\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659017-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHL_13-7c08ae-original-1772533115-1536x2303.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659017-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHL_13-7c08ae-original-1772533115-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659017-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHL_13-7c08ae-original-1772533115-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659017-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHL_13-7c08ae-original-1772533115-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659017-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHL_13-7c08ae-original-1772533115-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659017-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHL_13-7c08ae-original-1772533115-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659019-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_12-547091-original-1772533115.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"2303\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659019-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_12-547091-original-1772533115-1536x2303.jpg\" alt=\"One of a kind Scott Spark RC benefits World Bicycle Relief\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659019-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_12-547091-original-1772533115-1536x2303.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659019-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_12-547091-original-1772533115-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659019-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_12-547091-original-1772533115-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659019-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_12-547091-original-1772533115-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659019-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_12-547091-original-1772533115-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659019-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_12-547091-original-1772533115-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>“The bicycle itself is already an artwork on its own. Painting onto something that already existed was an interesting concept. It changes the way you see the object,” Smit said.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And he isn’t wrong. Along with the frame, the components Scott chose are a work of art themselves. In other words, they didn’t skimp, and the winner will get a truly spectacular race bike. Here’s the build:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Frame: </strong>SCOTT Spark RC HMX, Size M</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Fork: </strong>Rockshox Sid Ultimate Flight Attendant, 120mm Travel, 44mm Offset</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Rear Shock: </strong>Rockshox Sidluxe Flight Attendant 120mm Travel</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Remote: </strong>Sram Axs Pod Ultimate Controller</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659026-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_19-9a8383-original-1772533117-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1025\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659026-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_19-9a8383-original-1772533117-1536x1025.jpg\" alt=\"One of a kind Scott Spark RC benefits World Bicycle Relief\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659026-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_19-9a8383-original-1772533117-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659026-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_19-9a8383-original-1772533117-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659026-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_19-9a8383-original-1772533117-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659026-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_19-9a8383-original-1772533117-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659026-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_19-9a8383-original-1772533117-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659026-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_19-9a8383-original-1772533117-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659026-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_19-9a8383-original-1772533117-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659025-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_20-aaa2a7-original-1772533117.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1025\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659025-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_20-aaa2a7-original-1772533117-1536x1025.jpg\" alt=\"One of a kind Scott Spark RC benefits World Bicycle Relief\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659025-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_20-aaa2a7-original-1772533117-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659025-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_20-aaa2a7-original-1772533117-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659025-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_20-aaa2a7-original-1772533117-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659025-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_20-aaa2a7-original-1772533117-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659025-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_20-aaa2a7-original-1772533117-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659025-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_20-aaa2a7-original-1772533117-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659025-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_20-aaa2a7-original-1772533117-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Handlebar: </strong>Syncros Fraser Ic Sl Wc / -40° / 80mm / 700mm</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Seatpost: </strong>Rockshox Reverb Axs 31,6mm, 100mm</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Saddle: </strong>Syncros Belcarra R 1.0</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Grip: </strong>Syncros Silicone GR-M100 Grips</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Rear Derailleur: </strong>Sram XX Sl Eagle Transmission </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Shifter: </strong>Sram Axs Pod Ultimate</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659028-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_21-1ed4b9-original-1772533119-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1025\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659028-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_21-1ed4b9-original-1772533119-1536x1025.jpg\" alt=\"One of a kind Scott Spark RC benefits World Bicycle Relief\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659028-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_21-1ed4b9-original-1772533119-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659028-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_21-1ed4b9-original-1772533119-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659028-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_21-1ed4b9-original-1772533119-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659028-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_21-1ed4b9-original-1772533119-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659028-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_21-1ed4b9-original-1772533119-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659028-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_21-1ed4b9-original-1772533119-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/659028-LIONEL_SMIT_SPARK_2026_SCOTT_BIKE_PHOTO_BY_MICHAEL_RIEHLE_21-1ed4b9-original-1772533119-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Crank Set:</strong> Sram XX Sl Eagle Transmission Power Meter, 170mm/ 36T Chainring</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Chain: </strong>Sram XX Sl Eagle Transmission Flattop Chain</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Cassette: </strong>Sram XX Sl Eagle Transmission / 10-52t</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Brakes: </strong>Sram Motive Ultimate</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Wheels: </strong>Syncros Silverton SL</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tires: </strong>Maxxis Aspen 29×2.40wt Testpilot Exo/Tr </p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, again, ride it or hang it on the wall?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Nino Schurter and World Bicycle Relief</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Hand-painted-Scott-Spark-RC.jpg\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Hand-painted-Scott-Spark-RC.jpg\" alt=\"One of a kind Scott Spark RC benefits World Bicycle Relief\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Hand-painted-Scott-Spark-RC.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Hand-painted-Scott-Spark-RC-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Hand-painted-Scott-Spark-RC-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Hand-painted-Scott-Spark-RC-768x576.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The World Bicycle Relief is a nonprofit providing bicycles to rural, low-income communities. This helps people in communities overcome one of the greatest challenges they face: distance. Healthcare, education, economic opportunities, and other life essentials are simply more accessible by bike in many of these communities.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Both Scott and Nino have been long-time partners with the organization. In 2026, World Bicycle Relief is set to reach 1,000,000 donated bikes. And, their bike of choice is the durable, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/the-new-wbr-buffalo-bike-is-first-with-two-chain-two-speed-drivetrain/\">dual-chained Buffalo Bike</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>“World Bicycle Relief is an organization that is really close to my heart,” Nino said. “They do great things with the help of bicycles. It’s actually so cool to see what the bicycle can change in rural areas. If you get access to a bike, how the life can change of those families or this person…”</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Each entry supports the World Bicycle Relief and gets you closer to winning the bike. As of writing this, there are three months left until the winner is announced. Head to <em><a href=\"https://viprize.org/campaign/nino/?lang=en\">viprize.org</a>  </em>for the details and to enter.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/win-this-one-of-a-kind-scott-spark-rc-hand-painted-by-lionel-smit/\">Win a One-of-a-Kind Scott Spark RC; Nino Schurter Will Deliver </a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Travis Reill","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"17a31168472f44218eaed8dafc49cd23e1def336f4d44cafd8a8baff88da9f48","category":"Cycling"}